text: Isidoro Aquino Díaz (born 4 April 1966) is a former association footballer who played as a central defender for Sportivo Luqueño and the Paraguayan national football team. ==References== Category:Paraguayan footballers Category:Sportivo Luqueño players Category:Paraguay international footballers Category:Living people Category:1966 births Category:Association football defenders Category:Tigres UANL footballers Category:Cerro Porteño players
